<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Account Deactivated</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6200, #e65500);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Account Deactivated</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong>
                    <%= name %>
                </strong>,</p>
            <p>Your access to the application has been <strong>deactivated</strong> by the Admin.</p>
            <p>If you believe this was a mistake or need further information, please contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Thank you,<br>The <strong>
                    <%= domainName %>
                </strong> Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; <%= copyRightYear %>
                <%= domainName %>. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>